{
 "info": {
  "_postman_id": "a7c7bd7d-74d7-4bc3-bf9c-2b5d4481b7a7",
  "name": "E4 - Inventory Service (Grupo 7)",
  "description": "Coleccion de pruebas de integracion del Inventory Service (E4).\nCorrer SECUENCIALMENTE (Collection Runner). Cubre casos exitosos y fallidos:\nlogin admin real contra G2, lecturas publicas, carga de stock protegida (401/200),\nsincronizacion del catalogo de G3, y el caso critico de concurrencia\n(ultima unidad: 201 + 422) con confirmacion final.\nLos orderId son dinamicos: la coleccion es re-ejecutable sin limpiar la BD.",
  "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
 },
 "item": [
  {
   "name": "0. Login Admin (G2 Identity Service)",
   "event": [
    {
     "listen": "test",
     "script": {
      "type": "text/javascript",
      "exec": [
       "pm.test('Login OK (200)', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
       "const body = pm.response.json();",
       "pm.test('El usuario tiene rol admin', () => pm.expect(body.user.role).to.eql('admin'));",
       "pm.collectionVariables.set('access_token', body.access_token);",
       "// orderId dinamico: la coleccion es re-ejecutable sin limpiar la BD",
       "pm.collectionVariables.set('demoOrderId', 'ORD-PM-' + Date.now());"
      ]
     }
    }
   ],
   "request": {
    "method": "POST",
    "header": [
     {
      "key": "Content-Type",
      "value": "application/json",
      "type": "text"
     },
     {
      "key": "X-Consumer",
      "value": "postman-test-client",
      "type": "text"
     }
    ],
    "url": {
     "raw": "{{authUrl}}/auth/login",
     "host": [
      "{{authUrl}}"
     ],
     "path": [
      "auth",
      "login"
     ]
    },
    "body": {
     "mode": "raw",
     "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{adminEmail}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{adminPassword}}\"\n}",
     "options": {
      "raw": {
       "language": "json"
      }
     }
    }
   }
  },
  {
   "name": "1. Listar Inventario Completo",
   "event": [
    {
     "listen": "test",
     "script": {
      "type": "text/javascript",
      "exec": [
       "pm.test('Responde 200 OK', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
       "pm.test('Devuelve lista paginada (data + pagination)', () => {",
       "  const body = pm.response.json();",
       "  pm.expect(body).to.have.property('data').that.is.an('array');",
       "  pm.expect(body).to.have.property('pagination');",
       "});"
      ]
     }
    }
   ],
   "request": {
    "method": "GET",
    "header": [
     {
      "key": "X-Request-Id",
      "value": "{{$guid}}",
      "type": "text"
     },
